      <a href='#' data-toggle="modal" data-target="#freeShipping">
        FREE SHIPPING ON ALL US & CANADA ORDERS - <em>Need it by 12/25?</em>
      </a>
      </li>
    <li style='width:28%' class='hide email-form hidden-xs hidden-sm'>
      <div class='section-border'></div>
      <div class='mail-overlay'></div>
      <div class='submit-overlay'></div>
      <form action="http://zoraab.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=fdf8a5ce2518c055fc3be35d7&id=331f9e54ce" method="post" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" target="_blank">
        Save 10% Newsletter
